<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>앱주문 현관결제 - GS THE FRESH</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, target-densitydpi=medium-dpi" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,address=no,email=no" />
	<meta name="description" contents=""/>
	<meta name="keywords" contents=""/>
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.ico">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/fresh.css">
	<script src="../../js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="skipMenu"><a href="#container">본문 바로가기</a></div>
	<div class="wrapper">
		<header class="header">
			<h1>앱주문 현관결제</h1>
			<a href="#" class="btnBack">이전 페이지 이동</a>
			<button type="button" id="qrpop" class="btnQr" title="QR코드 팝업 열기">QR코드</button>
		</header>
		<!-- //header -->
		<section id="container" class="content">
			<div class="tabArea">
				<ul role="tablist">
					<li><!-- 선택시 aria selected값 true로 변경 -->
						<a href="#" role="tab" aria-selected="false">상품선택</a></li>
					<li><a href="#" role="tab" aria-selected="true">주문하기<em role="text"><span class="hide">주문 종류 수</span>10</em></a></li>
					<li><a href="#" role="tab" aria-selected="false">배송현황<em role="text"><span class="hide">신규 주문 추가 여부</span>N</em></a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="tabCont">
				<div class="odInfo line">
					<div class="titArea">
						<h2 class="title">주문정보 입력</h2>
						<a href="#" role="button" class="btnTS btnS">배송지관리</a>
					</div>
					<div class="odPerson">
						<h3 class="tit">주문하신 분</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>
								<span class="activeInput disabled">
									<label for="name01">홍길동</label>
									<input type="text" id="name01" disabled>
									<button type="button" class="delete">입력 내용 삭제</button>
								</span>
							</li>
							<li>
								<span class="activeInput">
									<label for="phoneNum01">핸드폰 번호<em>(숫자만 입력)</em></label>
									<input type="number" id="phoneNum01">
									<button type="button" class="delete">입력 내용 삭제</button>
								</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
						<h3 class="tit">받으시는 분</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>
								<span class="activeInput">
									<label for="name02">이름</label>
									<input type="text" id="name02">
									<button type="button" class="delete">입력 내용 삭제</button>
								</span>
							</li>
							<li>
								<span class="activeInput">
									<label for="phoneNum02">핸드폰 번호<em>(숫자만 입력)</em></label>
									<input type="number" id="phoneNum02">
									<button type="button" class="delete">입력 내용 삭제</button>
								</span>
							</li>
							<li>
								<span class="activeInput">
									<label for="txt02">배송시 요청사항을 입력해주세요</label>
									<input type="text" id="txt02">
									<button type="button" class="delete">입력 내용 삭제</button>
								</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="odList line">
					<h2 class="title">주문상품목록</h2>
					<!-- 주문상품목록 없는 경우 -->
					<div class="odListCon">
						<div class="noData">
							<p class="desc">선택하신 상품이 존재하지 않습니다.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="btnFixed">
							<div class="btnPrss">
								<button type="button" class="btnTP active" disabled>상품주문하기</button>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- //주문상품목록 없는 경우 -->
				</div>
				<!--//내용 -->
			</div>
		</section>
		<!-- //container -->
	</div>
	<!-- //wrapper -->
</body>
</html>